PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION ACT FEES REGULATIONS whereby immigrants who apply for an immigration visa from abroad will be required to pay the Right of Landing Fee before the visa is issued, or, where the application is made from within Canada, at the time they apply for landing.
